"USBBarCodeReader" is a library which purpose is to offer an easy and quick access to Usb BarCode devices.

Our support begin from API level 14 to 18 at the moment, mainly due to USB host feature, but we will improve earlier support soon.

#todo (by priority and possibility)#
*Add a discrimination sequence to improve barcode reader detection, and not only virtual or physical device.

